OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry day for most, with some
OL,6,Fsunny spells, but scattered afternoon
OL,7,Fshowers are possible in the north of
OL,8,Fthe region. Temperatures cooler than
OL,9,Fyesterday inland, and warmer near
OL,10,Fcoasts, however feeling fresher in
OL,11,Fgusty winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FAny lingering showers in the
OL,14,Fnorth dying out, leaving a dry night
OL,15,Fwith clear spells, and overnight
OL,16,Ftemperatures a little cooler than of
OL,17,Flate especially in rural spots. Wind
OL,18,Feasing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
