OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FDry with hazy sunshine and
OL,6,Fwarm or very warm for many again on
OL,7,FSaturday. However, cloud thickening
OL,8,Flater, with some outbreaks of
OL,9,Foccasionally heavy rain during the
OL,10,Fevening.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FTurning
OL,13,Fmore unsettled and cooler into the
OL,14,Fstart of next week. Temperatures
OL,15,Fnearer normal for the time of year.
OL,16,FBecoming breezy with outbreaks of
OL,17,Foccasionally heavy rain or showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
